@startuml
autonumber
actor "Admin Etablissement" as Admin
participant "Frontend" as Front
participant "API" as Back
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

title Scénario C : Validation d'un dossier (Admin)

== Réception ==
Admin -> Front: Consulte la liste des candidats "Soumis"
Front -> Back: GET /api/enrollments/?status=SUBMITTED
Back --> Front: Liste des dossiers

== Analyse ==
Admin -> Front: Ouvre le dossier de "Oussama"
Front -> Back: GET /api/enrollments/{id}/
Back --> Front: Détails + Liens vers PDF (CV, Lettre)
Admin -> Admin: Vérifie les pièces jointes

== Décision ==
Admin -> Front: Clique sur "Accepter"
Front -> Back: POST /api/enrollments/{id}/approve/
activate Back
Back -> DB: UPDATE Enrollment SET status='ACCEPTED'
Back -> Back: Trigger Email Notification (Accepté)
Back --> Front: 200 OK
deactivate Back

Front -> Admin: Confirmation visuelle
@enduml
